<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Delicake | Luxury Custom Cakes Bulawayo</title>
    <style>
        /* --- Reset & Global Styles --- */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Georgia', serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #fffcfc;
            color: #2c2527;
            line-height: 1.7;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* --- Navigation Bar --- */
        nav {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 1rem 3rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(191, 161, 171, 0.08);
        }

        .brand-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.2rem;
        }

        .logo-img {
            width: 55px;
            height: 55px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid #e5c4cd;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        }

        nav .logo-text {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #bfa1ab;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            align-items: center;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin-left: 2.5rem;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #5a4f52;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #caa5b0;
        }

        /* --- Hero Section --- */
        .hero {
            height: 80vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(44, 37, 39, 0.35), rgba(44, 37, 39, 0.35)), url('images/cake1.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-shadow: 2px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-style: italic;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 1px 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            max-width: 750px;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            text-shadow: 1px 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e5c4cd;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1.1rem 2.8rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(229, 196, 205, 0.4);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #caa5b0;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(202, 165, 176, 0.5);
        }

        /* --- Section General Styling --- */
        section {
            padding: 7rem 2rem;
            max-width: 1300px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 3.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 4.5rem;
            position: relative;
            color: #3e3336;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 60px;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: #e5c4cd;
            margin: 1rem auto 0;
        }

        /* --- Our Story Layout --- */
        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
            gap: 5rem;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .about-content h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #bfa1ab;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .about-content p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: #65585b;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }

        .info-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(191, 161, 171, 0.06);
            border-top: 4px solid #e5c4cd;
        }

        .info-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            color: #3e3336;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }

        .info-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            color: #5a4f52;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .info-card ul li {
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        /* --- Pricing Section Menu --- */
        .price-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(360px, 1fr));
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
        }

        .price-category {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(191, 161, 171, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(229, 196, 205, 0.15);
        }

        .price-category h3 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            color: #bfa1ab;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }

        .price-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: baseline;
            margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .price-item .item-name {
            color: #44383b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .price-item .item-dots {
            flex-grow: 1;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #caa5b0;
            margin: 0 12px;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        .price-item .item-cost {
            color: #2c2527;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        }

        .price-upgrade-box {
            background: #fff3f5;
            border: 1px solid rgba(229, 196, 205, 0.4);
            padding: 1.8rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #5a4f52;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(229, 196, 205, 0.1);
        }

        .price-upgrade-box strong {
            color: #bfa1ab;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* --- Portfolio Gallery --- */
        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1), box-shadow 0.4s ease;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(191, 161, 171, 0.18);
        }

        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
        }

        .cake-info {
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cake-info h3 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: #3e3336;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .cake-info p {
            color: #7c6e72;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-style: italic;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
        }

        /* --- Booking & Contact Form Layout --- */
        .contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr;
            gap: 5rem;
        }

        .contact-details {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 3.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(191, 161, 171, 0.05);
        }

        .contact-details h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #bfa1ab;
        }

        .contact-link {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            color: #44383b;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s, color 0.2s;
        }

        .contact-link:hover {
            color: #caa5b0;
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .contact-container {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 3.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(191, 161, 171, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(229, 196, 205, 0.2);
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
            color: #44383b;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .form-group input, .form-group textarea, .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid #ebdbe0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            background-color: #fffdfd;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
            color: #3e3336;
        }

        .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus, .form-group select:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #caa5b0;
        }

        button.btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        /* --- Terms & Conditions Section --- */
        .terms-container {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 3.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(191, 161, 171, 0.04);
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            color: #5a4f52;
            border: 1px solid rgba(229, 196, 205, 0.1);
        }

        .terms-container h3 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            color: #bfa1ab;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .terms-container ul {
            list-style-type: none;
        }

        .terms-container li {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            padding-left: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .terms-container li::before {
            content: "✦";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #e5c4cd;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .terms-container strong {
            color: #3e3336;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* --- Footer --- */
        footer {
            background-color: #2c2527;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        footer p {
            color: #d1c7c9;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        /* --- Responsive Viewport Tweaks --- */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .about-grid, .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3.5rem; }
            section { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
            .section-title { font-size: 2.6rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 3.2rem; }
            .hero h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            nav { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; padding: 1.5rem; }
            nav ul li { margin: 0 1.2rem; }
            .brand-container { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="brand-container">
            <img src="images/logo.jpg" alt="Delicake Logo" class="logo-img">
            <div class="logo-text">Delicake</div>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about">Story</a></li>
            <li><a href="#menu">Pricing</a></li>
            <li><a href="#gallery">Gallery</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Inquire</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero" id="home">
        <h1>Delicake</h1>
        <h2>Confection Made to Perfection</h2>
        <p>Designing sophisticated, bespoke custom cakes that taste as drop-dead gorgeous as they look.</p>
        <a href="#menu" class="btn">Explore The Menu</a>
    </header>

    <section id="about">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Art of Baking</h2>
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-content">
                <h3>Bespoke Baking from Bulawayo</h3>
                <p>Welcome to Delicake, founded and artfully directed by Head Baker Nyasha Marijeni. Operating from our specialized private studio in Bulawayo, Zimbabwe, we treat custom cake design as fine visual and edible art.</p>
                <p>Established in 2022, our core mission is simple: to make your celebration memorable. Every individual tier, floral arrangement, and delicate palette stroke is made exclusively by hand with premium ingredients.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <h4>Studio Consultations</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Mon, Tue, Thu, Fri, Sat:</strong> 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM</li>
                    <li><strong>Wednesday & Sunday:</strong> Closed to Public</li>
                    <li><em>*Pick-ups and menu tastings are scheduled strictly by appointment.</em></li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Studio Coordinates</h4>
                <p style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif; color:#65585b;">Bulawayo, Zimbabwe</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="menu" style="background: #fff6f7;">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Investment Menu</h2>
        
        <div class="price-grid">
            <div class="price-category">
                <h3>Gourmet Cupcakes</h3>
                <div class="price-item">
                    <span class="item-name">6 Cupcakes Boutique Pack</span>
                    <span class="item-dots"></span>
                    <span class="item-cost">$8</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-item">
                    <span class="item-name">12 Cupcakes Celebration Pack</span>
                    <span class="item-dots"></span>
                    <span class="item-cost">$15</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="price-category">
                <h3>Artisan Sponge Tiers</h3>
                <p style="font-family:'Georgia', serif; font-style:italic; color:#7c6e72; font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Includes traditional Vanilla Bean & Rich Chocolate cake bases</p>
                <div class="price-item">
                    <span class="item-name">6 inch (3 Premium Layers)</span>
                    <span class="item-dots"></span>
                    <span class="item-cost">$30</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-item">
                    <span class="item-name">7 inch (3 Premium Layers)</span>
                    <span class="item-dots"></span>
                    <span class="item-cost">$40</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-item">
                    <span class="item-name">8 inch (3 Premium Layers)</span>
                    <span class="item-dots"></span>
                    <span class="item-cost">$45</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-item">
                    <span class="item-name">10 inch (3 Premium Layers)</span>
                    <span class="item-dots"></span>
                    <span class="item-cost">$60</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="price-category">
                <h3>Traditional Fruit Cakes</h3>
                <div class="price-item">
                    <span class="item-name">6 inch Spiced Fruit Cake</span>
                    <span class="item-dots"></span>
                    <span class="item-cost">$40</span>
                </div>
                <div class="price-item">
                    <span class="item-name">8 inch Spiced Fruit Cake</span>
                    <span class="item-dots"></span>
                    <span class="item-cost">$50</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="price-upgrade-box">
            ✨ Elevate your sponge layers to our luxury flavors: <strong>Red Velvet / Rich Carrot / Classic Blackforest</strong> for an extra <strong>+$5</strong>.
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="gallery">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Masterpieces</h2>
        <div class="gallery-grid">
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="images/cake1.jpg" alt="Elegant Monogram Trio Wedding Cakes">
                <div class="cake-info">
                    <h3>Elegant Monogram Trio</h3>
                    <p>Flawless stark white frosting textures adorned with refined crest scrollwork.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="images/cake2.jpg" alt="Copper Ombre Wedding Cake with Warm Florals">
                <div class="cake-info">
                    <h3>Warm Autumn Wedding Tier</h3>
                    <p>Sophisticated multi-tier metallic copper gradient anchored by organic blooms.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="images/cake3.jpg" alt="Peppa Pig Fairy and Rainbow Themed Birthday Cake">
                <div class="cake-info">
                    <h3>Peppa Pig Fairy Magic</h3>
                    <p>Whimsical pastel fantasy scape crafted specifically for memorable bento birthdays.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-item">
                <img src="images/cake4.jpg" alt="Textured White Birthday Cake with Gold Crown and Pearls">
                <div class="cake-info">
                    <h3>Royal Crown Celebration</h3>
                    <p>Intricate, royal textured borders topped with a striking miniature gold tiara.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <h2 class="section-title">Commission Your Cake</h2>
        <div class="contact-grid">
            <div class="contact-details">
                <h3>Studio Desk</h3>
                <p style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif; color:#65585b; margin-bottom:2rem;">Ready to save your date? Reach our private studio desks directly or fill out our structural order inquiry form:</p>
                
                <a href="tel:+263715019907" class="contact-link">📞 Call Studio: +263 71 501 9907</a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/263775805912" target="_blank" class="contact-link">💬 WhatsApp Concierge: +263 77 580 5912</a>
                <a href="mailto:nyashamarijeni3031@gmail.com" class="contact-link">✉️ Email: nyashamarijeni3031@gmail.com</a>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-container">
                <form action="#" method="POST">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name">Full Name</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="Your Name">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">Email Address</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="name@domain.com">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="cake-type">Desired Size or Package</label>
                        <select id="cake-type" name="cake-type">
                            <option value="6-cupcakes">6 Gourmet Cupcakes Pack</option>
                            <option value="12-cupcakes">12 Gourmet Cupcakes Pack</option>
                            <option value="6-sponge">6" Sponge Tier (3 Layers)</option>
                            <option value="7-sponge">7" Sponge Tier (3 Layers)</option>
                            <option value="8-sponge">8" Sponge Tier (3 Layers)</option>
                            <option value="10-sponge">10" Sponge Tier (3 Layers)</option>
                            <option value="6-fruit">6" Spiced Fruit Cake</option>
                            <option value="8-fruit">8" Spiced Fruit Cake</option>
                            <option value="custom">Completely Custom Multi-Tier Concept</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="event-date">Date of Celebration</label>
                        <input type="date" id="event-date" name="event-date" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message">Design Details, Theme & Flavor Preference</label>
                        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required placeholder="Share your colors, flavor thoughts (e.g. standard vanilla/chocolate or premium upgrade like Red Velvet), and guest counts..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-submit">Send Studio Request</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="terms" style="padding-top: 0;">
        <div class="terms-container">
            <h3>Studio Policies</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Securing Your Calendar Slot:</strong> Due to the handcrafted nature of our premium designs, dates are strictly locked in only upon receipt of a **50% non-refundable deposit**. Final balances must be cleared prior to or during pick-up.</li>
                <li><strong>Design Adjustments:</strong> To ensure layout continuity and component prep times, changes regarding flavor profiles, decorations, or tier scaling must be submitted at least **7 days prior** to the event.</li>
                <li><strong>Collection Protocol:</strong> Pick-ups occur safely at our private Bulawayo studio by designated appointments. Once an art tier leaves our counter in pristine structure, transit mechanics and thermal management are the sole responsibility of the customer.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Delicake Boutique. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 0.8rem; font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #caa5b0;">Premium Handcrafted Custom Cakes | Bulawayo, Zimbabwe</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
